{"tid":2426432,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人可以幫我解一解夢","createTime":"2021-02-28T05:50:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T07:06:00.000Z","uid":19668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5a9ccef114f1268eccaacff61d9a29d0b5edbf9b","tid":2426432,"uid":19668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T05:50:39.000Z","msg":"是咁的，琴晚發咗個好奇怪嘅夢<br />\n同條女加個fd一齊去咗旅行<br />\n去到一個類似博物館嘅景點周圍都有好多戴黑超著老西嘅security 行嚟行去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個fd冇啦啦扮狗周圍柯尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住我見到個security 行到過嚟我就細細聲提佢:走呀xx！過到嚟呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (xx係佢個名)<br />\n佢就用狗嘅跑姿跑走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過跑得咁慢就緊係俾人捉到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後我就醒咗"},{"pid":"9f1035e66819f8e6568f2def7c5b23d37b1ecc74","tid":2426432,"uid":19668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T05:57:28.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb7cabd16f04bb402a835db79153aa983d8b2699","tid":2426432,"uid":369322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T05:59:55.000Z","msg":"你個friend係狗公"},{"pid":"23f78944f893c39839c29963954f76241cbabd06","tid":2426432,"uid":154478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T06:07:08.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪好大壓力<br />\n定驚比人綠"},{"pid":"a72c3b3ea15ca6c51a078ca504380af882437784","tid":2426432,"uid":19668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb7cabd16f04bb402a835db79153aa983d8b2699","tid":2426432,"uid":369322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T05:59:55.000Z","msg":"你個friend係狗公"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T06:25:34.000Z","msg":"唔係啦"},{"pid":"16cc087c52615e42c94508d13855c9b32d8cad75","tid":2426432,"uid":19668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23f78944f893c39839c29963954f76241